name: Maricopa
absentee_method: Released as a separate subtotal as first report of the night
poll_display_race: Polls closed at 9 p.m. Eastern time.
expectations_text_race: Maricopa County (Phoenix) released its final large set of results Saturday morning. Officials there said that a small number of provisional and other ballots that need additional time to process still remain.
